comments: Hield (IND) wraps an arm around Allen (CLE) and affects his ability to get to the pass.
LeVert (CLE) moves alongside Haliburton's (IND) path and marginal body contact occurs during the driving shot attempt.
Mitchell (CLE) and Turner (IND) come together in pursuit of the loose ball and marginal contact occurs.
The shot clock expires while IND is in possession of the ball.
Nesmith (IND) attempts to draw an offensive foul and the contact with Mobley (CLE) is marginal.
Hield (IND) legally contests Mobley's (CLE) layup attempt.
Nesmith (IND) is the last player to touch the ball before it goes OOB and possession should be given to CLE.
Mobley (CLE) brings his arm slightly forward and marginal contact occurs with Nesmith's (IND) arm during his driving shot attempt.
Levert (CLE) initiates contact with Nesmith's (IND) arm that affects his SQBR as the pass is made.
Nesmith (IND) contests the shot and initiates contact with Garland's (CLE) body, affecting the jump shot attempt.
Mitchell (CLE) initiates contact with Mathurin's (IND) wrist, which affects his driving shot attempt.
Mitchell (CLE) commits a take foul on Haliburton (IND).
